[assistant] Fixed the remaining issue in:
[assistant] 
[assistant] `tests/src/org.mongodb.morphia/morphia/1.3.2/build.gradle`
[assistant] 
[assistant] The earlier exclusion missed Morphia’s actual CGLIB artifact: `cglib:cglib-nodep`.
[assistant] 
[assistant] Updated dependency block now excludes both common CGLIB module names:
[assistant] 
[assistant] ```groovy
[assistant] testImplementation("org.mongodb.morphia:morphia:$libraryVersion") {
[assistant]     exclude group: "cglib", module: "cglib"
[assistant]     exclude group: "cglib", module: "cglib-nodep"
[assistant]     exclude group: "com.thoughtworks.proxytoys", module: "proxytoys"
[assistant] }
[assistant] ```
[assistant] 
